* A {{ill|Shrine|ja|神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shrine|qq=}} enshrining the child ({{ill|Mikogami|ja|御子神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mikogami|qq=}}) of the main deity ({{ill|Hongen|ja|本宮|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hongen|qq=}}). Examples include various {{ill|Wakamiya Shrines|ja|若宮神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakamiya Shrines|qq=}} and {{ill|Wakamiya Hachiman Shrines|ja|若宮八幡宮|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakamiya Hachiman Shrines|qq=}}.  
