ality in [[:en:Kurate District, Fukuoka|Kurate District]], Fukuoka Prefecture, now part of [[:en:Miyawaka|Miyawaka City]]. * {{ill|Wakamiya Town (disambiguation)|ja|若宮町 (曖昧さ回避)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakamiya Town (disambiguation)|qq=}} * {{ill|Wakamiya Town (Kanazawa City)|ja|若宮町 (金沢市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakamiya Town (Kanazawa City)|qq=}} - A locality in Kanazawa City, Ishikawa Prefecture. * {{ill|Wakamiya Town (Nakamura Ward, Nagoya City)|ja|若宮町 (名古屋市中村区)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakamiya Town (Nakamura Ward, Nagoya City)|qq=}} - A locality in {{ill|Nakamura Ward, Nagoya City|ja|名古屋市中村区|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nakamura Ward, Nagoya City|qq=}}, [[:en:Nagoya|Nagoya City]]. * Wakamiya Town (Yamaguchi City) - A locality in [[:en:Yamaguchi (city)|Yamaguchi City]], [[:en:Yamaguchi Prefecture|Yamaguchi Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Wakamiya Village (disambiguation)|ja|若宮村 (曖昧さ回避)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakamiya Village (disambiguation)|qq=}} * {{ill|Wakamiya Island|ja|若宮島|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakamiya Island|qq=}} - An island in [[:en:Iki, Nagasaki|Iki City]], [[:en:Nagasaki Prefecture|Nagasaki Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Wakamiya River|ja|若宮川|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wakamiya River|qq=}} - A {{ill|river|ja|河川|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/river|qq=}} in [[:en:Nihonmatsu, Fukushima|Nihonmatsu City]], [[:en:Fukushima Prefecture|Fukushima Prefecture]].
